message: /* Student activism */ Why this category and why not a complete history back to Vietnam?  PCC is in a contract conflict with teachers union; many sources one sided.  Will add facts on recent history, accomplishments.

/* Protest */  The entire Wiki article for PCC is grossly out of date, incomplete and inaccurate.  The creation of a "protest" section deeply politicizes this article by selecting a few  items. No mention of our veterans center, recent awards , etc.

/* Student activism */  - Deleted section that has an editorial voice. The author sounds anti-administration, instead of stating the facts clearly without bias, using such words as "embroiled." The author cites statements with editorial articles.
